                     <interp inst="t18360613-1479-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18360613-cd-91" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18360613-1479-offence-1 t18360613-cd-91"></join>4th of June</rs>, 1 print, framed and glazed, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18360613-name-646" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18360613-name-646" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
